Cats. The Doctors Whom. Science. Cute things. Life truths. Pixels. And spiders, sometimes, so keep that in mind.

My work with Vyc on a Kardasi conlang is here.

Cardassian meta is found mostly under cardassians or kardasi.

If you enjoy my fanfic, why not buy me a coffee?

summary: We’re not talking about this interview enough! Here’s some excerpts from it: "I decided early on, that Aziraphale loves...
caption:
We’re not talking about this interview enough!

Here’s some excerpts from it:

“I decided early on, that Aziraphale loves Crowley”.

“But then Crowley absolutely loves Aziraphale and hates that he loves him”.

"There is a, sort of, wonderful love story in this”.

And they’ve mentiones stuff about the fandom and how invested we all are in the relationship of those two. Even tho they’re not making the relationship explicit, is good to know it is in good hands and that the actors understand and acknowledge how important it is to the fandom :’)
